정 로그</h1><ul local-id=\"3745e652-a25c-4535-8d23-07bf78f44476\"><li local-id=\"50afbd8b-795d-4b2c-849e-0ac5afca14f7\"><p local-id=\"7bed87c11574\"><time datetime=\"2026-02-11\" local-id=\"2fc0662d-9b94-4e03-b6e8-2d15f7723e29\" />  문서 트리 구조 수정</p></li><li local-id=\"5076cb7cecf0\"><p local-id=\"d4de73b163f1\"><time datetime=\"2025-11-26\" local-id=\"7783da4f-993a-4781-8137-d4086fd7f569\" /> PUBG ID 디자인 시스템 등록</p></li></ul><p local-id=\"643a3a0b-0186-44fd-bc8f-09283a3cb404\" /><h1 local-id=\"0605ed99-7afd-42c1-9f92-1e28080ba350\">가이드 및 스펙확인</h1><ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"info\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:local-id=\"8d2ab18c-d887-49c1-b990-04b7a0902670\" ac:macro-id=\"12153499-9558-4683-88e1-7eeb92187143\"><ac:rich-text-body><p local-id=\"97a2d225-b930-4aeb-82fc-d5a4e4770f5b\">자세한 스펙은 아래 링크로 확인 가능합니다.</p><ul local-id=\"258c497a-12ad-4d04-b8b7-a4c293a08ba0\"><li local-id=\"72338102-b49f-45bb-a492-ca8ed25c3299\"><p local-id=\"1080d751-69c8-4d7e-aea4-7429e161dcb9\"><ac:emoticon ac:name=\"blue-star\" ac:emoji-shortname=\":figma:\" ac:emoji-id=\"c1fabecb-6925-40a3-9b8b-4f32041bb854\" ac:local-id=\"2157b465-1e09-4da1-ab58-dd75b5ddcd06\" ac:emoji-fallback=\":figma:\" /> <a href=\"https://www.figma.com/design/c8Qux8CARpdsaKg1KsUwMm/-%EA%B3%B5%ED%86%B5--ORDO-Design-system?node-id=49066-597\"><strong>PUBG ID 피그마 링크</strong></a></p></li><li local-id=\"f5d251a7-04b4-48cd-91e6-5c8edfe50ad4\"><p local-id=\"0786aa98-06c2-411f-a4a9-5a00848240d1\"><ac:emoticon ac:name=\"link\" ac:emoji-shortname=\":link:\" ac:emoji-id=\"1f517\" ac:local-id=\"1ef302fc-81ff-44cd-bc19-48e085a84470\" ac:emoji-fallback=\"\uD83D\uDD17\" /> <a href=\"https://ordo.pubg.io/?path=/story/functional-time-indicator--time-indicator\"><strong><ac:inline-comment-marker ac:ref=\"3d3d9bea-3baa-4563-b5ff-0d5b8e8d723c\">PUBG ID Storybook</ac:inline-comment-marker></strong></a><strong><ac:inline-comment-marker ac:ref=\"3d3d9bea-3baa-4563-b5ff-0d5b8e8d723c\"> (등록후 변경 필요)</ac:inline-comment-marker></strong></p></li><li local-id=\"de518965-776a-4346-ac13-16f91d3c156d\"><p local-id=\"b91dabdd-1bcd-47be-b97f-f8d0a253b2de\"><ac:emoticon ac:name=\"link\" ac:emoji-shortname=\":link:\" ac:emoji-id=\"1f517\" ac:local-id=\"788799a0-697b-49b4-86ea-47c54ded40a5\" ac:emoji-fallback=\"\uD83D\uDD17\" /> <a href=\"https://krafton.atlassian.net/wiki/x/owwZLg\" local-id=\"e371a5c6-6aa8-45f3-a9c1-2d8bbb7bbd66\" data-card-appearance=\"inline\">https://krafton.atlassian.net/wiki/x/owwZLg</a> </p></li></ul></ac:rich-text-body></ac:structured-macro><ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"panel\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:local-id=\"834f059a2e60\" ac:macro-id=\"4405ac73-b76f-4d6c-b2ed-3d8bec2f01e5\"><ac:parameter ac:name=\"panelIcon\">:bulb:</ac:parameter><ac:parameter ac:name=\"panelIconId\">1f4a1</ac:parameter><ac:parameter ac:name=\"panelIconText\">\uD83D\uDCA1</ac:parameter><ac:parameter ac:name=\"bgColor\">#FFFAE6</ac:parameter><ac:rich-text-body><p local-id=\"602153c18be0\">디자인 변경 사양 체크 포인트</p><ul local-id=\"b0ebb60d5dec\"><li local-id=\"634aff40ea9f\"><p local-id=\"05aaf7bc8222\">PUBG ID 메달 영역의 경우 메달의 사이즈에 따라 겹칠 가능성이 있습니다.</p></li><li local-id=\"7f5b298bba1b\"><p local-id=\"3b972191ced2\">기존 피쳐에 적용된 PUBG ID 의 전체 사이즈의 변화는 없습니다. (네임플레이트 BG 영역)</p><ul local-id=\"af18332a4b25\"><li local-id=\"1632a4db3869\"><p local-id=\"a08d30911849\">내부 유저 닉네임 및 텍스트 사이즈 변경함</p></li><li local-id=\"a75529c1b3db\"><p local-id=\"6ae02683271b\">아이콘 등 세부 사이즈 변경함</p></li></ul></li></ul></ac:rich-text-body></ac:structured-macro><h1 local-id=\"d267dccc-3072-480f-9a3b-bb707a730269\"><br />정의</h1><p local-id=\"020e80b8-cbcf-4ca0-91ad-ec140ab7738b\"><ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"status\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"5e9fd804-41c2-4314-a73f-4e0323afc112\"><ac:parameter ac:name=\"title\">complex</ac:parameter><ac:parameter ac:name=\"colour\">Yellow</ac:parameter></ac:structured-macro><ac:inline-comment-marker ac:ref=\"83facadb-7adb-4fa7-87da-856d0629d997\">  플레이어의 프로필 및 온/오프라인 상태 등 플레이어의 정보를 알려주는 아웃게임 컴포넌트</ac:inline-comment-marker></p><ac:image ac:align=\"center\" ac:layout=\"center\" ac:original-height=\"348\" ac:original-width=\"701\" ac:custom-width=\"true\" ac:local-id=\"9648affc-83d0-4a33-b0e4-2d8ba04e1b6a\" ac:alt=\"image-20251222-063416.png\" ac:width=\"743\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"image-20251222-063416.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"1\" /></ac:image><p local-id=\"f48b4c06-5f52-4f8b-af33-c444ac1b044e\"><ac:emoticon ac:name=\"blue-star\" ac:emoji-shortname=\":alert:\" ac:emoji-id=\"aa871de9-765d-4e85-941b-30dd58635fc2\" ac:local-id=\"d5475ef3-ce33-4484-a3e3-5d2f86b9e721\" ac:emoji-fallback=\":alert:\" /><strong> <span style=\"color: rgb(255,86,48);\">인게임과는 별개의 컴포넌트로 관리하여 아웃게임만 취급합니다.</span></strong></p><p local-id=\"f6c33c08-635f-482d-a25a-313ca69139d5\" /><h1 local-id=\"559c5242-580a-489c-aa35-f1719b898d40\">개발 사양</h1><h2 local-id=\"6eb144d7-488e-434c-8d9f-02131bd52ae2\">일반 규칙</h2><ul local-id=\"1daa77e4-96a1-45c6-9b38-5e6ea9b420a1\"><li local-id=\"d0e8776f-f954-4d52-8d1c-65fa362136a3\"><p local-id=\"c07a53bb-1334-4f9f-93ee-95874a64285d\">PUBG ID의 내부 구성 요소는 모두 Property On/Off로 조정하여 사용 가능</p></li><li local-id=\"3e8644fc-ba6e-4b0e-bd66-0a7c421b4186\"><p local-id=\"2a1e0fe6-8672-4721-8b26-5984986406f3\">세가지 사이즈 타입으로 나누어 사용 가능(Small/Medium/Large)</p></li></ul><p local-id=\"dd28f42c-7f5e-4152-9743-54031ccad5e6\" /><h2 local-id=\"f9b9f0f9-7665-424a-88d4-8dd6a2131339\">속성별 규칙</h2><table data-table-width=\"760\" data-layout=\"center\" ac:local-id=\"518ac1e6-e2e6-4fe2-8d52-b3d882c1a327\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 130.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 222.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 407.0px;\" /></colgroup><tbody><tr ac:local-id=\"767c151f-d5af-403d-94f0-c7133c022515\"><th ac:local-id=\"e6394bdc-8612-44af-ac4f-5e67605a21a0\"><p local-id=\"ecb70410-aba5-4f81-9d9e-67c5f13a4407\"><strong>속성</strong></p></th><th ac:local-id=\"bfc3f8cc-3898-4ad9-9123-ca6918558e7c\"><p local-id=\"9a2de2d7-5d51-4a0e-bd50-0c536f5f9e5e\"><strong>분류</strong></p></th><th ac:local-id=\"280f2d3e-0353-4a39-a8d5-41c8290035c2\"><p local-id=\"762b7a24-5617-4701-b9c9-70c878bbfadd\"><strong>규칙</strong></p></th></tr><tr ac:local-id=\"540058ea-e6a9-43d8-b6ed-e33d29d91691\"><td ac:local-id=\"fa3ad5b4-8b7c-491b-812b-c5848edc5f0e\"><p local-id=\"a3867e93-e924-456a-a3de-e313a238f9e6\">네임플레이트 아이디 (nameplateId)</p></td><td ac:local-id=\"e341525a-eafb-4e6e-b715-2ea09e8f3e36\"><p local-id=\"94782648dfb6\" /></td><td ac:local-id=\"26442af5-aa2b-4ed2-9427-c5c0b2c9bbcf\"><ac:image ac:align=\"center\" ac:layout=\"center\" ac:original-height=\"1451\" ac:original-width=\"2523\" ac:custom-width=\"true\" ac:local-id=\"56325e65-eed5-4729-86ee-1c395c84cb1b\" ac:alt=\"image-20260114-072655.png\" ac:width=\"488\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"image-20260114-072655.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"1\" /></ac:image><ul local-id=\"a62df7b8-cc6f-4eb4-9592-3c56d9a2698d\"><li local-id=\"31c211a6-e42d-4737-8250-dbe04675c055\"><p local-id=\"c2661517-4f17-4de5-a88d-164dd73455b3\">네임플레이트는 PUBG ID의 배경 요소로써 사용됨 </p></li><li local-id=\"4b204267-65dc-4fea-aa03-e376980d0e5a\"><p local-id=\"b2a0abbf-48fd-4348-bcc0-520aa1317e97\">네임 플레이트  항상 장착 상태가 기본 (장착 해제 상태 없음)</p><ul local-id=\"d3784ab6-46a6-4de3-ad6d-4a94ed9e73f3\"><li local-id=\"71d49ddb-a520-435a-ad3e-a193ea7b2867\"><p local-id=\"05e04cd0-2595-43be-9f20-fe40373043f8\">소셜형에서 오프라인시 기본 회색 배경으로 제공 (예외)</p></li></ul></li><li local-id=\"2fea80a0492e\"><p local-id=\"932d9de98601\">장착한 nameplateId에 따라 해당하는 네임플레이트 이미지 또는 동영상을 보여준다. </p></li></ul></td></tr><tr ac:local-id=\"7de32ef14114\"><td ac:local-id=\"08f855cbcebf\"><p local-id=\"1a26f3f0e9b8\">애니메이션 재생 여부</p><p local-id=\"6ffee18ef7cd\">(enableAnimation)</p></td><td ac:local-id=\"bc91e8edf2e1\"><ul local-id=\"211299707359\"><li local-id=\"83551166fa90\"><p local-id=\"1b9b2dcae51d\">true</p></li><li local-id=\"364b963ceb93\"><p local-id=\"7cbcceb7d258\">false   </p></li></ul></td><td ac:local-id=\"19fdc0249095\"><ul local-id=\"f676bdd1-005f-40e5-9e1c-32aee6623555\"><li local-id=\"9e10774c-312f-42e8-9d24-e668faaea67c\"><p local-id=\"4d3db640a6dc\">PUBG ID 요소 중 네임플레이트와 엠블럼은 이미지 타입과 애니메이션 타입이 존재한다.</p></li><li local-id=\"648e9ad3711d\"><p local-id=\"896c9cbee692\">true일 경우 동영상을 재생하고, false일 경우 이미지를 사용한다.</p></li></ul></td></tr><tr ac:local-id=\"ae59c8ec-916a-4db4-83ed-504369c5df3f\"><td ac:local-id=\"8aa58ad4-dfec-45d3-947b-40a647dfdb0e\"><p local-id=\"8879dd4e-198b-4c0d-a5bb-277fea57471e\">플레이어 닉네임</p><p local-id=\"a588f3483766\">(nickname)</p></td><td ac:local-id=\"65919458-8004-435f-b8a0-e692ede22106\"><ul local-id=\"036993831b3d\"><li local-id=\"14c6afb4b6bf\"><p local-id=\"5849623410bf\">string</p></li></ul></td><td ac:local-id=\"979e2e93-7647-42ce-ad67-890b305ab3af\"><ac:image ac:align=\"center\" ac:layout=\"center\" ac:original-height=\"1760\" ac:original-width=\"2803\" ac:custom-width=\"true\" ac:local-id=\"d6aa20d1-ecfb-460b-b1cd-7e0fd9c883ca\" ac:alt=\"image-20251222-064332.png\" ac:width=\"490\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"image-20251222-064332.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"1\" /></ac:image><ul local-id=\"1aebe582-f019-4d45-80fe-953d77754383\"><li local-id=\"ef4f3275-e001-4219-bd91-84355ab497af\"><p local-id=\"92694134-c41d-4015-943f-7253abc50103\">플레이어 닉네임은 PUBG ID 좌상단 영역에 위치함</p></li><li local-id=\"4ad74831-35a3-445b-be7f-281ca83fc713\"><p local-id=\"62811ca1-f5ff-45d2-83c4-8f58aee15331\">닉네임은 최대 대문자 W 16자까지 노출 가능</p></li></ul></td></tr><tr ac:local-id=\"871377c35caf\"><td ac:local-id=\"b8934c183934\"><p local-id=\"0f38ff5c4059\">오리진 타입</p><p local-id=\"1c78324115a2\">(OriginType)</p></td><td ac:local-id=\"ec8b028c0adb\"><ul local-id=\"aaa7cbcbd70c\"><li local-id=\"8180321eb0b1\"><p local-id=\"4767b4dc21a9\">xbox </p></li><li local-id=\"42ad25fdb272\"><p local-id=\"62e8fbd817e3\">playstation</p></li><li local-id=\"2be74f93f6aa\"><p local-id=\"04bffbc1df1c\">&hellip;</p></li></ul></td><td ac:local-id=\"1d3c23318beb\"><ac:image ac:align=\"center\" ac:layout=\"center\" ac:original-height=\"1760\" ac:original-width=\"2803\" ac:custom-width=\"true\" ac:local-id=\"868e6ea22c48\" ac:alt=\"image-20251222-064332.png\" ac:width=\"490\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"image-20251222-064332.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"1\" /></ac:image><ul local-id=\"bec1a058-547e-463b-980a-b493ad179872\"><li local-id=\"5c7e11f6-60e0-4a3d-892a-96983eff1bfc\"><p local-id=\"765e75a9274e\">콘솔 유저인 경우 닉네임 옆에 플랫폼 아이콘 노출됨</p></li></ul></td></tr><tr ac:local-id=\"4dc9f08c-a3b6-4b23-9444-0bcc7a0bea6f\"><td ac:local-id=\"31542d2d-5d9e-4a69-ae5b-917b27157221\"><p local-id=\"b26e23d4-4479-4378-af74-463e41f9e42b\">메달</p><p local-id=\"4c5cfc9382fe\">(favoriteMedals)</p></td><td ac:local-id=\"df4089cf-f708-460c-9496-71885547bf49\"><p local-id=\"ee23a0ea-d846-42a0-a471-9579d6533e39\" /></td><td ac:local-id=\"366d1ecd-1cba-404e-9363-9057f9d1f5c0\"><ac:image ac:align=\"center\" ac:layout=\"center\" ac:original-height=\"1760\" ac:original-width=\"2803\" ac:custom-width=\"true\" ac:local-id=\"1fdcc70b-c6a0-4c71-9872-70f8213a1c68\" ac:alt=\"image-20251222-064355.png\" ac:width=\"488\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"image-20251222-064355.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"1\" /></ac:image><ul local-id=\"856f0398-1d22-4f97-a24a-e1ddcb8b0d57\"><li local-id=\"0e27d7fe-e413-41d6-95e4-0c7787ef0714\"><p local-id=\"1dba5bfd-f482-43d4-be5b-4fa267eb977a\">PUBG ID에 메달을 장착하여 노출가능</p></li><li local-id=\"fb1f7ba1-6064-4343-9f44-8c65f68469c8\"><p local-id=\"5bd0630d-342f-42eb-810b-4ea33087158b\">PUBG ID 우측 끝단에 위치함</p></li><li local-id=\"a9074b52-ea5b-49fe-ac07-9d79a48f12da\"><p local-id=\"95f0c697-6f95-431b-bb88-6f8bdf9eb259\">2개까지 노출할 수 있으며, 하나 추가될 때 우측정렬되어 위치함</p></li></ul></td></tr><tr ac:local-id=\"be11c5a2-35bd-4808-a59d-f00b74bc111e\"><td ac:local-id=\"9d5286fb-4711-4d81-9ac8-e41249ca458b\"><p local-id=\"c798fd62-0df6-4f30-baf8-d61fecc249b6\"><ac:inline-comment-marker ac:ref=\"8ac0b567-92f9-4e32-8277-9af79ea987dd\">연결 상태</ac:inline-comment-marker></p><p local-id=\"3ac4d5dfaf55\">(userConnectionStatus)</p></td><td ac:local-id=\"4958bd0a-30b8-4938-843c-1d3ea04cbfeb\"><ul local-id=\"7e4e9cd664fa\"><li local-id=\"1fb1