1c\"><ac:parameter ac:name=\"title\">default</ac:parameter><ac:parameter ac:name=\"colour\">Green</ac:parameter></ac:structured-macro></p></li><li local-id=\"94e5c2a9-52e8-4ebd-b3e2-a1797aebb40b\"><p local-id=\"5ab06d35-e5de-4b0c-9425-d371df88635f\">true</p></li></ul></td><td ac:local-id=\"aa32d6f8-e4f7-4e39-9383-0636c6dec224\"><ac:image ac:align=\"center\" ac:layout=\"center\" ac:original-height=\"1253\" ac:original-width=\"2523\" ac:custom-width=\"true\" ac:local-id=\"ae2c17c1-2f1c-44bc-8534-c3b78d6f8b4c\" ac:alt=\"image-20260114-055038.png\" ac:width=\"488\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"image-20260114-055038.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"1\" /></ac:image><ul local-id=\"f5575b4c-36e1-4344-9363-d2bb3196103f\"><li local-id=\"22d2b602-8dd0-4086-aa01-a3dcf8e2eceb\"><p local-id=\"9f91a6b5-2b3b-4976-8aef-7fb265b0e294\">콘솔 플랫폼에서 특정 유저 음소거 처리시 노출</p></li><li local-id=\"bda35fda-7328-49c7-b7f0-aeb873ca3b38\"><p local-id=\"8a5552a5-d2bf-4d07-8fca-9c8018d2d745\">평판, 클랜 관리자, 음소거 아이콘 순서로 노출됩니다. </p></li></ul></td></tr><tr ac:local-id=\"63f7c578-735e-4d33-996e-e41b70eb4aa4\"><td ac:local-id=\"6bda980199c7\"><p local-id=\"8854f15c-231b-439f-9bf0-b575da1f77a7\">서바이벌 마스터리 (티어+레벨)</p><p local-id=\"c0a0dbab0da6\">(survivalMastery)</p></td><td ac:local-id=\"2677a03d5f50\"><p local-id=\"f47e8fbb-0a30-4e7d-adb6-dfca711a6701\" /></td><td ac:local-id=\"3c4d9257-6de5-4f17-803a-08b0635ce6d0\"><ac:image ac:align=\"center\" ac:layout=\"center\" ac:original-height=\"1393\" ac:original-width=\"2803\" ac:custom-width=\"true\" ac:local-id=\"5992dc69-3e28-4c14-b45f-cc4f453635c6\" ac:alt=\"image-20251222-065254.png\" ac:width=\"488\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"image-20251222-065254.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"1\" /></ac:image><ul local-id=\"4ec783c2-b381-4278-827e-94174d964955\"><li local-id=\"5c519f20-c1cc-46aa-90cf-9215e49cda87\"><p local-id=\"b3892cef-22b0-4905-9076-9aad965096db\">티어 정보와 레벨 정보를 포함한다</p></li><li local-id=\"5ab18e845eea\"><p local-id=\"6f970e6b4042\">닉네임 하단에 노출되며, 만약 소셜확장형처럼 유저상태(온